code: export function initRange(domain,range){switch(arguments.length){case 0:break;case 1:this.range(domain);break;default:this.range(range).domain(domain);break;}return this;}export function initInterpolator(domain,interpolator){switch(arguments.length){case 0:break;case 1:{if(typeof domain==="function")this.interpolator(domain);else this.range(domain);break;}default:{this.domain(domain);if(typeof interpolator==="function")this.interpolator(interpolator);else this.range(interpolator);break;}}return this;}
